Some necessary tokens for better experience:

Futanari version (important!):

  1. Change "FemEred" to "FutEred" after "Eredar". It give access Lora to second subset with futa content.

  1. Try these prompts and add weights to it if you feel you need it:

    futanari, erection, huge penis, huge testicles, animal penis

    futanari, large penis, large testicles, erection, animal penis

  2. Sometimes prepending these prompts before (masterpiece:1.4) gives good results.

Alternatively you can use another LoRA for horse penises from here, they work well!

Also LoRA trained with some NSFW arts but I didn't test in special poses.

Advices for better experience:

use highres.fix (If you are sure that your prompt is easy for SD); I prefer Remacri for this time.

use extention "after detailer" (very useful extension for faces).

use SD Upscale script in img2img (For me 1.25-1.5x with AnimeSharp, UltraSharp or fatal anime is good on 0.15-0.3 denoising strengh); For this time I prefer Remacri.

use Ultimate SD Upscale script in img2img with controlnet (tile) for more details if you upscale to 4K or more.

Use inpaint and sketch (or Photopea) for other details;

Use Photoshop / Photopea extension.

I will be glad to receive feedback from you and a demonstration of your art with my LoRA!
